# Shared Directory

The [visionspark/lib/shared/](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared) directory contains shared components:

- [main_scaffold.dart](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared/main_scaffold.dart): Main app layout scaffold
- [connectivity_service.dart](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared/connectivity_service.dart): Network connectivity management
- [offline_screen.dart](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared/offline_screen.dart): Offline state UI
- [utils/](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared/utils): Utility functions (snackbar_utils.dart)
- [notifiers/](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared/notifiers): State management (subscription_status_notifier.dart)

